    "Page Four Rickenbacker Calls On Congress To ReImplement Monroe Doctrine And To Drive Communism Out Ot Cuba Forthwith Utter Disregard By Kennedy Of U S Foreign Policy Is Roundly Denounced Captain Eddie Rickenbacker a hero in both World Wars and a former Presi dent of the Eastern Air Lines is calling on Congress to see that the Monroe Doc trine is reimplemented and that Com munism is removed from Cuba forth with According to Rickenbacker the Na tion is in jeopardy and he says In our own hemisphere the Monroe Doctrine strictly and immediately en forced is the only policy which stands between freedom and ultimate Com munist takeover of all of Latin America Kennedy Administration His statement follows The Kennedy administration has com mitted the final betrayal of Cuban hopes for freedom by its order to block the activities of exiled Cuban freedom fight ers to liberate their nation from com munism By the same token President Kennedy is underwriting continued So viet control over Cuba with the armed might of the United States Thus a mas sive and fatal historic contradition is per petrated by the young men who control the executive branch of our Govern ment a"
